snippet.title: Get Out Of My Store! - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Get Out Of My Store! is a game developed in under 2 months for the Amstrad CPC  464, a computer from the eighties!

Visit us on itch.io: https://pyrobombastic-games.itch.io/g...

Download the game for FREE and try it on an emulator!

This game was made for the #CPCRetroDev contest.

By PyroBombastic Games
